GET /api/1/auth  -> get user session
POST /api/1/auth -> login user
DELETE /api/1/auth -> logout logged user


POST /api/1/user  -> register new user
PUT /api/1/user/(:id) -> update user settings
DELETE /api/1/user/(:id) -> delete user

POST /api/user/remind -> remind password 




